(fifthQuint)Safety Study of DanshenDuofensuanyan(a Chinese Medicine Injection)Used in Hospitals in China.

 It is very common that Chinese Medicine Injection used in hospitals in mainland China.

 However safety problems rose in recent years.

 There could be many uncertain factors influence Chinese Medicine Injection in clinical practice.

 In order to ensure the safety of public drug use and lower drug-induced risks, a registry study for DanshenDuofensuanyan injection safety surveillance with 30000 patients will be conducted from Jan.

2013 to Dec.

2015.

 Eligibility criteria Patients who will use DanshenDuofensuanyan injection in selected hospitals.

